{"tid":1524091,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[旺角,太子恐襲] 事件始末","createTime":"2019-08-31T16:39:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-01T04:19:00.000Z","uid":37673,"like":40,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"552fff41585bbc32b40ca5ed585b2b4455aa2032","tid":1524091,"uid":37673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T16:39:12.000Z","msg":"本身手足都係諗住轉場或者散<br />\n諗住旺角轉車 一落車就話狗落月台大家即刻上返兩邊去太子嘅車<br />\n<br />\n之後去到太子 荃灣線嘅車就開咗<br />\n剩低觀塘線 但停咗好耐無開<br />\n手足覺得唔對路就開始換衫<br />\n<br />\n然後黨鐵就響alarm 話要閂站 <br />\n有啲市民就屌鳩手足搞事 <br />\n<br />\n未夠五分鐘 速龍就落嚟 <br />\n見到逃跑,有gear,黑衫嘅就追<br />\n之後就係大家見到新聞嘅事<br />\n<br />\n冷氣軍師 你哋嘅一言一行其實好影響在場手足嘅心情<br />\n當你親眼見到速龍 喺地鐵站怎樣捉自己身邊嘅手足 <br />\n你又乜都做唔到嗰種感受 你係冇可能知道係點<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我只係希望大家無條件支持大家 呢一場仗好撚難打 但我哋知道我哋團結就會贏 分化就會輸<br />\n<br />\n我已經好尊重你哋亂鳩咁講嘢<br />\n希望你哋下次會改善 大家一齊進步<br />\n一步一步咁贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8132f52c0cd3c3bf4b72fcbf4d37890cc65e687","tid":1524091,"uid":95487,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T16:39:44.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">試下找不同？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/H8DUzH7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FH8DUzH7.jpg&h=4b81709e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Lxqsagt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLxqsagt.jpg&h=281798cd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"83f739b12e053dd4ede3f6a125316a9614d823c6","tid":1524091,"uid":236437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T16:40:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ca242fc2dcdf0b1902f9a37765f984fbd781503","tid":1524091,"uid":37673,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T16:42:48.000Z","ms